export AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=XXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
export AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=XXXXXXXXXXX
export AWS_DEFAULT_REGION=XXXXXXXXXXXXXX


pass the above commands, then there is no to mention region,accesskey and secret key in tf scripts.
To make them permenant for a user, in the user's home directory, in bash_profile, define the above 
variables and export them. then environmental variables will be saved for that user.
